column5: Or should it be humane?  Just curious was the dawg catcher around this weekend.  Haven't heard one bark yet     Whopper
LOL....Phil I expect they are still recovering  Maureen

Yup we had the Dawg in the house. He was just as wound up as he was the year before and one of the best roommates you could ask for. I will let him fill in the gaps with his own story and pictures.   Art
Good deal Art!  I was just trying to poke him with a stick
